<section class="py-5 aboutwistech" style="margin-top: 70px;">
      <div class="container">
       
        <div class ="row">
          <div class="col-lg-9 col-sm-12">
             <h2 style="font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif; text-align: left; color: #fd5d65; font-size: 25px;" class="js-reveal">
         Donate Goods to Help a Great Cause</h2>
        <hr align="left" width="10%" class="divederlined">
           <p style="font-weight: 300; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; text-align: left; color: #000000; font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;" class="js-reveal">
           WHEN YOU DONATE goods to “BE A BLESSING MISSION” those items are shipped to Africa. Most of the donated goods are given to orphanages and schools. Then the rest are sold and the proceeds are used as education fund for the brilliant but needy student, community projects, etc. 
           </p>
           <ul style="font-weight: 300; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; text-align: left; color: #000000; font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;">
           	<li>Clothing & Shoes</li>
           	<li>Furniture</li>
           	<li>Household Goods</li>
           	<li>Electrical appliances</li>
           	<li>Childrens Stationary like books, pens, pencils, scientific calculators, Back packs(school bags), COmputers and laptops.</li>
           </ul>

           <p style="font-weight: 300; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; text-align: left; color: #000000; font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;">
           	<span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: #fd5d65;">To donate goods to Be a Blessing Mission kindly call 757-217-8836 or schedule a schedule a pickup. You can also mail your item to:</span><br>
			Be a Blessing Mission,<br>
			3824 Virginia Beach Blvd,<br>
			Virginia Beach, Virginia 23452.<br><br>
			Your donation supports “Be a Blessing Mission” poverty fighting work in the African continent. Be a Blessing Mission delivers lasting change to some of the African’s poorest communities. We place a special focus on working alongside Charitable Organizations that supports orphans/children. 
		  </p>
           
          <div class="col-lg-3 col-sm-12">
           <!--  <img src="logowebbie.png" width="200px" height="200px" class="img-fluid"> -->
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-12">
          	<div class="row">
          		<h5>Enter your details and Goods you are donationg</h5><br>
          		<div class="col-lg-9">
          			<%= form_for(@good) do |f| %>
  <% if @good.errors.any? %>
    <div id="error_explanation">
      <h2><%= pluralize(@good.errors.count, "error") %> prohibited this good from being saved:</h2>

      <ul>
      <% @good.errors.full_messages.each do |message| %>
        <li><%= message %></li>
      <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label>Name</label>
    <%= f.text_field :name, :class => "form-control", :placeholder => "Your Name" %>
  </div>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label>Email</label>
    <%= f.text_field :email, :class => "form-control", :placeholder => "Your Email" %>
  </div>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label>Phone number</label>
    <%= f.text_field :phone, :class => "form-control", :placeholder => "Your Phone number" %>
  </div>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label>Items to Donate</label>
    <%= f.text_area :itemsdonate, :class => "form-control", :placeholder => "What items are you going to donate?" %>
  </div>

  <div class="form-group">
    <%= f.submit "Submit", :class => "btn btn-primary" %>
  </div>
<% end %>
